{"title":"Bone \u0026 Joint Supplements","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"flax-seeds","title":"Raw Unroasted Flax Seeds naturally rich in Omega-3 fatty acids Helps in cholesterol levels, weight loss or management and strong Bones","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0cm; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;\"\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 116%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;\"\u003eIf a healthy snack option is what you seek, which can not only reduce your hunger but also provide essential nutrients, neuherbs \u003cspan style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eflax seeds are your answer. \u003cspan style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eneuherbs ’ organic, raw, and unroasted flax seeds provide Omega-3 fatty acids, like ALA, protein, calcium, and fiber. This makes it a fantastic meal maker for weight loss management and optimal heart health. It can help reduce inflammation, manage cholesterol levels, and regulate BP. The soluble fiber in neuherbs flaxseeds helps slow down digestion, regulate blood sugar levels, and reduce hunger, while the insoluble fiber promotes better bowel movements. You can add neuherbs Organic Flaxseeds to your smoothies, overnight oats, burger dough, bread dough, pancake batter, and nutrition bars or you can have them raw as your go-to snack, to avail maximum benefits for your health. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9.0pt; line-height: 116%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Value Pack - (1 KG)=Recommended","offer_id":40971567726762,"sku":"NFS1000","price":299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/1kgflax_5.jpg?v=1731058797"},{"product_id":"organic-chia-seeds-health-boost-weight-loss-1","title":"Organic Chia Seeds for Weight Loss \u0026 Boost Health","description":"\u003cp style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;\"\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 116%; font-family: 'Arial',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;\"\u003eChia Seeds are a powerhouse of nutrients, primarily dietary fiber, omega –3 fatty acids, protein, magnesium, calcium, and antioxidants. These essential nutrients help manage weight, strengthen bones, regulate blood sugar levels, and improve skin health. Rich in both fiber and protein, including chia seeds in your daily diet can effectively curb hunger pangs, potentially reducing chances of overeating and late-night cravings. Rich in Omega 3 fatty acids and high in antioxidants, neuherbs \u003cspan style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"\u003e \u003c\/span\u003enatural, raw \u0026amp; unroasted chia seeds offer a powerful punch of nutritional wellness. Our chia seeds for weight loss are premium grade and sourced organically from the best farms in India. Chia seeds have a mild nutty flavour and can be used in smoothies, oatmeal toppings, salads, or porridges, or can be added in water as well. You can also add neuherbs Chia Seeds to baked goods for tasty yet healthy nutritional punch.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Starter Pack - (500GM)","offer_id":44202808737962,"sku":"NCS500","price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Value Pack - (1KG)","offer_id":44266511925418,"sku":"NCS1000","price":699.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/chia_500g_front.jpg?v=1728478343"},{"product_id":"organic-flax-seeds-weight-loss","title":"Organic Flax Seeds: Rich in Omega-3 for Weight Loss \u0026 Health","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph;\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 116%; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;\"\u003eFlax seeds have gained widespread popularity over the last few years - and rightfully so! It is not only rich in fiber and omega-3 fatty acids like ALA, but it also contains certain ingredients like protein and calcium that allow it to be the go to source of wellness for those looking to make better lifestyle choices. It has been known to reduce inflammation, help manage cholesterol levels while also regulating blood sugar levels or pressure. To add to its benefits, it further helps manage digestion and hunger levels by keeping you satiated for longer periods of time. neuherbs Flaxseeds are sourced from the most potent sources across India, and are 100% natural to help your health unlike any other ingredient. You can add neuherbs Flax Seeds to your smoothies, overnight oats, bread dough, baked food items or make nutritious bars out of it to avail benefits of several other ingredients alongside. Flax seeds can also be added to your daily life as a snack, a fistful of which can help your wellness like never before.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Smart Pack - (400 GM)","offer_id":44266376528042,"sku":"NFS400","price":149.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Artboard15_2.jpg?v=1726146160"},{"product_id":"organic-chia-seeds-health-boost-weight-loss","title":"Chia Seeds for Weight Loss \u0026 Boost Health","description":"\u003cp class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-ideograph; margin: 12.0pt 0cm 12.0pt 0cm;\"\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 116%; font-family: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;\"\u003eChia seeds are a good source of several essential nutrients and antioxidants which help in weight management and other important aspects of our daily lives. Which is why we bring to you neuherbs Chia Seeds —- sourced organically from purest farms across India, we bring to you our 100% natural, raw \u0026amp; unroasted Chia seeds to make your daily meals and snacking more nutritious and healthy! Chia seeds are known for their richness in fiber, protein and essential omega-3 fatty acids, which provide several health benefits to you in the longer run. Available with a mild nutty flavour, neuherbs Chia seeds can be added to your meals or be enjoyed as a snack separately as well.\u003cspan style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"\u003e  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"EN-US\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Starter Pack - (200GM)","offer_id":44266406805674,"sku":"NCS200","price":169.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/Artboard5_391d4a3d-8f47-45d4-b87e-4606c6ac471f.jpg?v=1715578403"},{"product_id":"true-calcium-plant-based-vitamin-d3","title":"True Calcium Tablets with Plant Vitamin D3 for Stronger Bones","description":"\u003cp class=\"sort-description\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAn amazing 3-in-1 supplement for daily bone and muscle care, neuherbs True Calcium supplement by neuherbs contains 1000 mg of calcium in a more bioavailable Calcium Citrate form, more-bioavailable Vitamin D3, and natural Magnesium. All three vital nutrients work together to maintain strong bones, increase bone density, support muscle, tendon relaxation and contraction, reducing the risk of fractures and brittle bones later in life. True Calcium, the plant-based calcium tablets, help fill the daily calcium gap in adults. Paired with Vitamin D3 it supports better absorption of calcium in the body. Th unique combination of magnesium \u0026amp; calcium in these calcium tablets for bones works synergistically to support muscles contraction, relaxation \u0026amp; improve overall flexibility.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Neuherbs","offers":[{"title":"Monthly Pack - (60 Tablets)","offer_id":44271815033002,"sku":"NTC60","price":299.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"Saver Pack - (120 Tablets)","offer_id":46152267366570,"sku":"NTC60P2","price":598.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0577\/6162\/8330\/files\/true_calcium_tablets_1.png?v=1747133307"}],"url":"https:\/\/neuherbs.com\/collections\/bone-joint-supplements.oembed","provider":"Neuherbs","version":"1.0","type":"link"}